data.name: aquisição_btn_aditamento_guide
data.value: When clicking on the AMENDMENT button, the system enters into a contractual amendment mode allowing the user, upon justification, to change the contract properties that impact the results of the calculations performed by the system.

data.name: aquisição_btn_historico_guide
data.value: By clicking on the HISTORY button, the system shows in chronological order the history of all the modifications suffered by the contract since its creation.

data.name: aquisição_btn_replicar_guide
data.value: By clicking on the DUPLICATE button, the system creates a copy (clone) with the main properties of the contract being edited. This feature is widely used in the creation of contracts that have similar characteristics.

data.name: aquisição_delete_texto
data.value:
By clicking on the OK button the contract will be deleted from the system if and only if it fully meets the following conditions:

. There is no End of Exercise note.
. It does not have an Accounting Interface annotation.
. There is no note on Financial Transactions (Cash Monitoring).
. There is no commitment and / or payment authorization (APR) note committed or carried out.

If all of the above conditions are met, the Real, Nominal, Inflated, Currency and USGaap scenarios will be excluded:
. All records in the accounting statement.
. All financial statement records.
. All cash flow records.
. The contract and its properties (general information, classification, basis of negotiation, linked funds and attachments).
